#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:0
msgid "Setting up a binary cache for store objects"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:0
msgid "Nix, caching"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:9
msgid "Setting up an HTTP binary cache"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:11
msgid ""
"A binary cache stores pre-built [Nix store objects](https://nix.dev/manual/"
"nix/latest/store/store-object) and provides them to other machines over the "
"network. Any machine with a Nix store can be a binary cache for other "
"machines."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:14
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "簡介"

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:16
msgid ""
"In this tutorial you will set up a Nix binary cache that will serve store "
"objects from a NixOS machine over HTTP or HTTPS."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:18
msgid "What will you learn?"
msgstr "您將會學到什麼？"

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:20
msgid "You'll learn how to:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:21
msgid "Set up signing keys for your cache"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:22
msgid "Enable the right services on the NixOS machine serving the cache"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:23
msgid "Check that the setup works as intended"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:25
msgid "What do you need?"
msgstr "您需要什麼？"

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:27
msgid "A working [Nix installation](<install-nix>) on your local machine"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:29
msgid "SSH access to a NixOS machine to use as a cache"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:31
msgid ""
"If you're new to NixOS, learn about the [module system](module-system-"
"tutorial) and configure your first system with [](nixos-vms)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:33
msgid "(optional) A public IP and DNS domain"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:35
msgid ""
"If you don't host yourself, check [NixOS-friendly hosters](https://wiki."
"nixos.org/wiki/NixOS_friendly_hosters) on the NixOS Wiki. Follow the "
"tutorial on [](provisioning-remote-machines-tutorial) to deploy your NixOS "
"configuration."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:38
msgid "For a cache on a local network, we assume:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:39
msgid "The hostname is `cache` (replace it with yours, or an IP address)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:40
msgid "The host serves store objects via HTTP on port 80 (this is the default)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:42
msgid "For a publicly accessible cache, we assume:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:43
msgid "The domain name is `cache.example.com` (replace it with yours)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:44
msgid ""
"The host serves store objects via HTTPS on port 443 (this is the default)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:46
msgid "How long will it take?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:48
msgid "25 minutes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:50
msgid "Set up services"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:52
msgid ""
"For the NixOS machine hosting the cache, create a new configuration module "
"in `binary-cache.nix`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:54
msgid ""
"{ config, ... }:\n"
"\n"
"{\n"
"  services.nix-serve = {\n"
"    enable = true;\n"
"    secretKeyFile = \"/var/secrets/cache-private-key.pem\";\n"
"  };\n"
"\n"
"  services.nginx = {\n"
"    enable = true;\n"
"    recommendedProxySettings = true;\n"
"    virtualHosts.cache = {\n"
"      locations.\"/\".proxyPass = \"http://${config.services.nix-serve."
"bindAddress}:${toString config.services.nix-serve.port}\";\n"
"    };\n"
"  };\n"
"\n"
"  networking.firewall.allowedTCPPorts = [\n"
"    config.services.nginx.defaultHTTPListenPort\n"
"  ];\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:77
msgid ""
"The options under [`services.nix-serve`] configure the binary cache service."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:79
msgid ""
"`nix-serve` doesn't support IPv6 or SSL/HTTPS. The [`services.nginx`] "
"options are used to set up a proxy, which does support IPv6, to handle "
"requests to the hostname `cache`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:86
msgid ""
"There is an [optional HTTPS section](https-binary-cache) at the end of this "
"tutorial."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:89
msgid "Add the new NixOS module to the existing machine configuration:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:91
msgid ""
"{ config, ... }:\n"
"\n"
"{\n"
"  imports = [\n"
"    ./binary-cache.nix\n"
"  ];\n"
"\n"
"  # ...\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:103
msgid "From your local machine, deploy the new configuration:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:105
msgid "nixos-rebuild switch --no-flake --target-host root@cache\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:110
msgid ""
"The binary cache daemon will report errors because there is no secret key "
"file yet."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:113
msgid "Generate a signing key pair"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:115
msgid ""
"A pair of private and public keys is required to ensure that the store "
"objects in the cache are authentic."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:117
msgid ""
"<!-- TODO: link to the remote builds tutorial for the case where store "
"objects are signed after building them -->\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:119
msgid ""
"To generate a key pair for the binary cache, replace the example hostname "
"`cache.example.com` with your hostname:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:121
msgid ""
"nix-store --generate-binary-cache-key cache.example.com cache-private-key."
"pem cache-public-key.pem\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:125
msgid ""
"`cache-private-key.pem` will be used by the binary cache daemon to sign the "
"binaries as they are served. Copy it to the location configured in `services."
"nix-serve.secretKeyFile` on the machine hosting the cache:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:128
msgid ""
"scp cache-private-key.pem root@cache:/var/secrets/cache-private-key.pem\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:132
msgid ""
"Up until now, the binary cache daemon was in a restart loop due to the "
"missing secret key file. Check that it now works correctly:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:135
msgid "ssh root@cache systemctl status nix-serve.service\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:140
msgid ""
"[](custom-binary-cache) using `cache-public-key.pem` on your local machine."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:143
msgid "Test availability"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:145
msgid ""
"The following steps check if everything is set up correctly and may help "
"with identifying problems."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:147
msgid "Check general availability"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:149
msgid ""
"Test if the binary cache, reverse proxy, and firewall rules work as intended "
"by querying the cache:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:151
msgid ""
"$ curl http://cache/nix-cache-info\n"
"StoreDir: /nix/store\n"
"WantMassQuery: 1\n"
"Priority: 30\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:158
msgid "Check store object signing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:160
msgid ""
"To test if store objects are signed correctly, inspect the metadata of a "
"sample derivation. On the binary cache host, build the `hello` package and "
"get the `.narinfo` file from the cache:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:163
msgid ""
"$ hash=$(nix-build '<nixpkgs>' -A pkgs.hello | awk -F '/' '{print $4}' | awk "
"-F '-' '{print $1}')\n"
"$ curl \"http://cache/$hash.narinfo\" | grep \"Sig: \"\n"
"...\n"
"Sig: cache.example.org:"
"GyBFzocLAeLEFd0hr2noK84VzPUw0ArCNYEnrm1YXakdsC5FkO2Bkj2JH8Xjou+wxeXMjFKa0YP2AML7nBWsAg==\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:170
msgid ""
"Make sure that the output contains this line prefixed with `Sig:` and shows "
"the public key you generated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:173
msgid "Serving the binary cache via HTTPS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:175
msgid ""
"If the binary cache is publicly accessible, it is possible to enforce HTTPS "
"with [Let's Encrypt](https://letsencrypt.org/) SSL certificates. Edit your "
"`binary-cache.nix` like this and make sure to replace the example URL and "
"mail address with yours:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:178
msgid ""
"   services.nginx = {\n"
"     enable = true;\n"
"     recommendedProxySettings = true;\n"
"-    virtualHosts.cache = {\n"
"+    virtualHosts.\"cache.example.com\" = {\n"
"+      enableACME = true;\n"
"+      forceSSL = true;\n"
"       locations.\"/\".proxyPass = \"http://${config.services.nix-serve."
"bindAddress}:${toString config.services.nix-serve.port}\";\n"
"     };\n"
"   };\n"
"\n"
"+   security.acme = {\n"
"+     acceptTerms = true;\n"
"+     certs = {\n"
"+       \"cache.example.com\".email = \"you@example.com\";\n"
"+     };\n"
"+   };\n"
"\n"
"   networking.firewall.allowedTCPPorts = [\n"
"     config.services.nginx.defaultHTTPListenPort\n"
"+    config.services.nginx.defaultSSLListenPort\n"
"   ];"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:203
msgid "Rebuild the system to deploy these changes:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/binary-cache-setup.md:205
msgid "nixos-rebuild switch --no-flake --target-host root@cache.example.com\n"
msgstr ""

